query:
SELECT
                u.id,
                u.display_name,
                u.slug,
                u.created_at,
                it.reset_timestamp,
                it.notes
            FROM users u
            INNER JOIN incident_timers it ON u.id = it.user_id
            INNER JOIN user_preferences up ON u.id = up.user_id
            WHERE up.timer_is_public = true
              AND up.timer_show_in_list = true
            ORDER BY it.reset_timestamp DESC
            LIMIT $1 OFFSET $2
